title: Star Trek The Next Generation Season 1.1080p.Bluray.DTS.5.1.x264
description:
Here is a blu-ray rip of Star Trek TNG Season 1. This is the largest season so far due to the grainyness of the show. All episodes have all subtitles featured on disc and original DTS 5.1 audio. Lots of people don't have DTS-HD Master Audio equipment. Episodes were encoded with constant rate factor and varying bitrate for quality emphasis.
